[[File:Transorb.jpg|thumb|right|''Transorb'', a modified ''Rho''-class shuttle.]]
The '''''Rho''-class shuttle''' was one of the precursors to the [[Lambda-class T-4a shuttle/Legends|''Lambda''-class shuttles]] which were produced during the time of the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic]].

A great many of these vessels, of which thousands were made, were scrapped or sold off as surplus to commercial companies during the days of the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Old Republic]]. A few still remained in [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] hands by the time of the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]], and served in outlying [[Sector/Legends|sector]] fleets of [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]]. One such ship, the ''[[Transorb]]'', was in use by the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]].

